<font color="#FF0000">&quot;CANNON FODDER&quot; A JOKE!</font><br>
<tt>Mon Dec 16  8:13:13 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
&quot;Cannon Fodder&quot; is a slick work of imaginative fiction.  As a *Real* veteran who spent the entire year of 1970 in Vietnam, I think that Mr. Coleman may have been in the Army, and may have spent time in Vietnam, but his alleged experiences are a far cry from what I remember, and my memories are still quite strong.  <br><br>
I regret that anyone reading this book who is *not* a Vietnam veteran will be severely misled.  <br><br>
Two thumbs down...
<p><code>-- lbruce@somtel.com  (A Real Veteran) </code><p>


